title: A1534 820-00244-A no disk
message:
Hi,

I have an A1534 820-00244-A that stoped to recognize the disk with no reason at all.

PP1V8_S0SW_SSD_COLD = 0V
PP0V9_S0SW_SSD_FIXED = 0V

I don't know where to start. Can you help?

title: A1534 820-00244-A no disk
message:
CPU and SSD are common failures for A1534.
Is not a good idea to waste time on it.
Can come back with other issue and client will claim for warranty.
